description: Ex-president Poroshenko sees Russian influence at work in the new administration.
title: Ukraine's Zelensky accused by ex-leader of hosting Russian 'fifth column'
title_page: Ukraine's Zelensky accused by ex-leader of hosting Russian 'fifth column' - BBC News
maintext: "I was one of the happiest [people] in the world if I was wrong," he said. "But unfortunately this is true. The fifth column of the Russian federation are now playing a very important role in Ukraine."
